<c74object name='sp.lpgcore~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>A poly~ of a vactrol/low pass gate model</digest>
    <description>A poly~ of a vactrol/low pass gate model.</description>
    <discussion>    <h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
    <p>The <o>sp.lpgcore~</o> object is the underlying <o>poly~</o> that handles the actual filter/gate part of the low pass gate algorithm. It is wrapped up inside a <o>poly~</o> to be enable upsampling for better sounding results. It's not intended to be used on its own, but rather it is the core component of <o>sp.lpg~</o>.</p>
</discussion>

